W_n=\int_0^{\pi/2} \sin^n x = \left. -\sin^{n-1}x\cos x \right|_0^{\pi/2} + (n-1)\int_0^{\pi/2} \sin^{n-2} x (1- \sin^2 x) d x = (n-1) W_{n-2} - (n-1) W_n.
